>这些惊人的统计数据得益于所有<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/counter-strike-global-offensive"><em>《反恐精英：全球攻势》</em></a>玩家都将<em>《反恐精英 2》</em>免费添加到他们的库中。 </p><figure id="attachment_3418961" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3418961" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3418961" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-AWP.jpg" alt="《反恐精英 2》。图片来源：Valve。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-AWP.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-AWP-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-AWP-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-AWP-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-AWP-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-AWP-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3418961" class="wp-caption-text"> 《反恐精英 2》。图片来源：Valve。</figcaption></figure><p>此外，玩家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-wont-take-away-your-csgo-skins-3418940">在<em>《全球攻势》</em>中令人垂涎的皮肤收藏已转移</a>到升级版<em>《反恐精英 2》</em>中，现在在先进引擎中看起来好多了。</p><p> Valve 保证说：“除了支持旧模型和饰面之外，所有库存武器都已升级为高分辨率模型，并且一些武器饰面利用了这些新模型。”</p><p>由于这些游戏内物品的价值可达数万英镑，如果开发商不允许继承旧皮肤，那可能会给开发商带来灾难。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/tony-hawks-pro-skater-1-and-2">《托尼霍克的职业滑板手 1 + 2》</a></em>将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/tony-hawks-pro-skater-1-2-is-coming-to-steam-3505248">下周登陆 Steam</a> ，包括标准版和数字豪华版，现在其 Epic Games Store 独占权已经结束。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-launches-with-a-massive-player-count-3505709">《反恐精英 2》发布后拥有大量玩家，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
