“我认为科特在某种程度上取笑这一点，因为他不像科特那样是个怪人。而且他也很嫉妒。我认为库尔特有点嫉妒戴夫，因为戴夫确实有他的表演。”</p><p>您可以在下面收听完整的采访。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify Embed：“Kurt 嫉妒 Dave”：“In Utero”三十年后的启示" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/7EWZ7Mwy60LCMq6p0HO0h8?utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>早在 2019 年，Nirvana 的前经理丹尼·戈德伯格就表示，科本很清楚格罗尔的声乐天赋， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kurt-cobain-knew-good-singer-dave-grohl-says-former-nirvana-manager-2471342">暗示两人之间可能存在“一丝嫉妒”</a> 。</p><p>格罗尔在 2005 年表示，“有时候库尔特对我打鼓的方式非常不满意”，并补充道： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-338-1277686">“</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-338-1277686">我能听到他在谈论他认为我有多糟糕……”</a>但他永远不会对我说。”</p><p> Foos 主唱当时解释说，这些问题是在“In Utero”时代出现的。 “就在那时，我认为库尔特对乐队中发生的事情感到不满，”他继续说道。</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-says-he-doesnt-get-caught-up-in-wondering-what-kurt-cobain-wouldve-thought-of-foo-fighters-2873722">格罗尔表示，他不会好奇科本会对喷火战机的音乐有何看法</a>。 “你不能用别人的标准来创造或判断任何东西，”他<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/foo-fighters-cover-interview-2021-medicine-at-midnight-2872365">在接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>说道。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-says-kurt-cobain-was-the-greatest-songwriter-of-our-generation-2882421">格罗尔此前曾称赞科本是“我们这一代最伟大的歌曲作家”</a> 。他补充道：“我非常自豪地说，我必须成为他的鼓手，每晚都会演奏这些歌曲。”</p><div id="imgpreloader"><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nirvana-interview-krist-novoselic-in-utero-30-years-ai-music-new-reunion-3501830">Nirvana 乐队的克里斯特·诺沃塞利克 (Krist Novoselic) 最近接受<em>NME</em>采访，谈论了乐队影响深远的第三张也是最后一张专辑《In Utero》的 30 周年纪念</a>。</p></div><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nirvana-biographer-claims-kurt-cobain-was-jealous-of-dave-grohl-3505658">《涅槃》传记作者声称库尔特·科本“嫉妒”戴夫·格罗尔</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 PlayStation 负责人 Jim Ryan 即将退休https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/playstation-head-jim-ryan-is-retiring-3505646?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=playstation-head-jim-ryan-is-retiringImogen Donovan Thu, 28 Sep 2023 09:17:50 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPS5 https://www.nme.com/?p=3505646 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="吉姆·瑞恩.图片来源：Alex Wong / Getty Images。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Ryan 于 1994 年加入索尼互动娱乐欧洲公司</p><p>即将<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/playstation-head-jim-ryan-is-retiring-3505646">退休的 PlayStation 负责人吉姆·瑞安 (Jim Ryan)</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="吉姆·瑞恩.图片来源：Alex Wong / Getty Images。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/PlayStation-boss-Jim-Ryan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>自 2019 年起担任<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sony-interactive-entertainment">索尼互动娱乐</a>总裁兼首席执行官的吉姆·瑞安 (Jim Ryan) 宣布将于 10 月辞去职务。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/marvels-spider-man-2-is-shaping-up-to-be-a-heroic-sequel-3497940">《漫威蜘蛛侠 2》将成为一部英雄续集</a></strong></li></ul><p>Ryan 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/playstation">PlayStation</a>工作了近 30 年，于 1994 年加入，并于 2016 年成为欧洲业务的全球销售和营销主管。</p><p>他负责监督<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a>的发布，而 PS5 却因 2020 年冠状病毒危机的影响而受阻。在调查<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sony-wont-share-ps6-details-with-activision-if-its-owned-by-microsoft-3459615">收购</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision">动视暴雪</a>可能对竞争产生影响的过程中，瑞安还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/playstation-says-call-of-duty-offer-by-microsoft-is-inadequate-on-many-levels-3306571">公开反对</a>微软收购动视暴雪。</p><p>索尼在一份声明中（来自<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-09-27/playstation-boss-jim-ryan-is-retiring-from-sony-in-march?srnd=technology-vp"><em>彭博社</em></a>）表示：“索尼互动娱乐 (SIE) 今天宣布，SIE 总裁兼首席执行官吉姆·瑞安 (Jim Ryan) 决定于 2024 年 3 月退休，此前他在 PlayStation 业务工作了近三十年。” </p><figure id="attachment_3483327" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3483327" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3483327" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/marvels-spider-man-2-accessibility-slow-option.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/marvels-spider-man-2-accessibility-slow-option.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/marvels-spider-man-2-accessibility-slow-option-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/marvels-spider-man-2-accessibility-slow-option-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/marvels-spider-man-2-accessibility-slow-option-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/marvels-spider-man-2-accessibility-slow-option-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/marvels-spider-man-2-accessibility-slow-option-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3483327" class="wp-caption-text"> 《漫威蜘蛛侠 2》图片来源：索尼</figcaption></figure><p>该公司继续说道：“为了支持 Ryan 先生的过渡，索尼集团公司总裁、首席运营官兼首席财务官 Hiroki Totoki 将于 2023 年 10 月起担任 SIE 董事长。”</p><p> “自 2024 年 4 月 1 日起，Totoki 先生将被任命为 SIE 临时首席执行官，同时继续担任索尼集团公司的现任职务。”</p><p>瑞安在自己的声明中解释了他个人和职业生活在欧洲和北美的平衡如何给他带来了压力。</p><p> “我很高兴有机会在一家非常特别的公司从事我喜欢的工作，与优秀的人才和令人难以置信的合作伙伴一起工作。但我发现越来越难以调和欧洲生活和北美工作，”他说。 </p><figure id="attachment_3465133" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3465133" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3465133" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3465133" class="wp-caption-text"> PlayStation 5 图片来源：Triyansh Gill，来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p>最后，他感谢索尼集团公司首席执行官吉田健一郎对他的“信任”以及作为“一位极其敏感和支持性的领导者”的指导。</p><p>据称，在美国正式推翻宪法规定的堕胎权之前，瑞安<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2022-05-12/sony-playstation-staff-fume-over-ceo-s-abortion-comments">向索尼员工发送了一封电子邮件</a>，建议他们“尊重意见分歧”，然后告诉他们他的宠物猫的生日庆祝活动。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/guerrilla-games">Guerrilla Games</a>发布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/horizon-forbidden-west-is-coming-to-pc-next-year-3505195"><em>《地平线：西部禁域》完整版</em></a>，该版本即将登陆<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/PC">PC</a>和 PS5。</p><p>即将<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/playstation-head-jim-ryan-is-retiring-3505646">退休的 PlayStation 负责人吉姆·瑞安 (Jim Ryan)</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
